name: tc001_Dashboard

testSteps.description: Given that i am in the the procurement portal
And click the menu icon in the procurement portal home page
And scroll down to recent orders section of the procurement portal home page
And scroll down to recent orders section of the procurement portal home page
And click see all orders in the procurement portal home page
And check the pre filled branch plant buyer and date from fields
And switch back to the dashboard page of the procurement portal
And scroll down to pie chart section of the procurement portal home page
And click the buyers filter in the procurement portal home page
And click the exit icon of the buyers filter modal in the procurement portal home page
And click the see all list in the procurement portal home page
